tune.name: Mikael Georgii's Compliments to Angela Young
tune.author: Mikael Georgii
tune.content:
\relative f'' <<
  {
    \clef treble
    \key f \minor
    \time 6/8

    \partial 8 c8 |
    \repeat unfold 2 {
      aes8 c c f, c' c |
      bes8 c c g c c |
      c8 des c c e g |
      f4. f4 ees8 |
      \break

      des8 f f bes, c des |
      c8 f f aes, bes c |
    } \alternative { {
      b8 c des g, b g' |
      c,4 c8 bes aes g |
      \bar "||" \break
    } {
      c8 des c c des e |
      f4. f4 ees8 |
      \bar "||" \break
    } }

    des8 f f bes, f' f |
    c8 f f aes, f' f |
    c8 des c g aes bes |
    c4. c4 f8 |
    \break

    des8 f f bes, f' f |
    c8 f f aes, f' f |
    b,8 c des g, b g' |
    c,4 c8 bes aes g |
    \bar "||" \break

    aes8 c c f, c' c |
    bes8 c c g c c |
    c8 des c c e g |
    f4. f4 ees8 |
    \break

    des8 f f bes, c des |
    c8 f f aes, bes c |
    c8 des c c des e |
    f4. f4
    \bar "|."
   }

  \new ChordNames {
    \chordmode {
      s8 |
      f2.:m | c4.:7/g c:7/e | c:7 c:7/e | f:m f:m/aes |
      bes4.:m bes:m/g | f:m/aes f:m | g g/b | c:7 c:7/e |

      f2.:m | c4.:7/g c:7/e | c:7 c:7/e | f:m f:m/aes |
      bes4.:m bes:m/g | f:m/aes f:m | c2.:7 | f:m |

      bes2.:m | f4.:m/aes f:m | | c2. | f4.:m f/a |
      bes4.:m g:dim | f:m/aes f:m | g g:7 | c c:7 |

      f2.:m | c4.:7/g c:7/e | c:7 c:7/e | f:m f:m/aes |
      bes4.:m bes:m/g | f:m/aes f:m | c:7 c:7/e | f:m
    }
  }
>>
